    <item>
      <title>Snowflake 的 Frank Slootman 将从首席执行官职位上退休，将继续担任董事会主席</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/snowflake-misses-estimates-says-ceo-slootman-to-step-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[软件制造商 Snowflake Inc. 公布了令人失望的销售预测，并宣布首席执行官弗兰克·斯洛特曼 (Frank Slootman) 辞职，该公司在尾盘交易中暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/snowflake-misses-estimates-says-ceo-slootman-to-step-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 21:12:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国月球登陆器在完成历史性任务后消失在黑暗中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/-plucky-moon-lander-fading-out-after-six-days-on-lunar-surface</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周在历史性登月过程中失事的美国航天器将于周三晚上关闭，结束一项备受关注的任务，该任务推动了私营部门的太空探索，但未能实现客户的总体目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/-plucky-moon-lander-fading-out-after-six-days-on-lunar-surface</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 20:55:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
